checkoutservice` 的支付模块在高负载下需求性能优化。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"latency_spike\", \"checkoutservice->checkoutservice\", \"cartservice->redis\", \"checkoutservice->payment\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著延迟在 PaymentService/Charge 操作\",\n      \"evidence\": \"正常: 13865.84ms, 异常: 39617.37ms, 倍数: 2.86\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"与 redis 的调用延迟显著增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HMSET 正常: 1573.06ms, 异常: 15320.04ms, 倍数: 9.74\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些迹象表明，主要的瓶颈来自于 `checkoutservice` 中的支付服务和 `cartservice` 同 `redis` 的交互。"}
